# Unit tests

Run with `uv run pytest` (dev dependency group; no Jetson hardware or inference server needed).

## Scope (`tests/`)

- **Coordinate math** — letterbox, overlay, visualization coords (`test_visualize_coords.py`)
- **Focus/crop logic** — box hit-test, padding, crop→frame mapping, submodel routing (`test_focus_crop.py`)
- **CHARM OCR matching** — fuzzy name matching (`test_charm_ocr.py`)

## When editing tested code

- Update or add tests for coordinate math, focus/crop, or CHARM matching changes
- Run `uv run pytest` before finishing
- Do not add tests that require camera, TRT, or network unless the user asks

## Out of scope for unit tests

Validate camera + inference end-to-end via `pss-live-demo` or `pss-phone-demo`.
